HEADS AA

// HEAD 1 IS FOR READING, HEAD 2 IS FOR WRITING

// FIRST WE READ ALL LINES AND COPY THEM INTO THE ROW ABOVE
// THEN, WE REMOVE THE LAST ROW
// THEN WE TRIM THE FIRST ROW DOWN TO THE SHORTEST POSSIBLE
// LASTLY, WE TRIM ALL OTHER ROWS

// 1. READING
START ** READING ** SU

READING #* READING   *# RR
READING =_ READING   *= RR
READING == READING   ** RR
READING =| READING   ** RR
READING |* MOVE_LEFT *| LL
READING _* TRIMMING ** US

MOVE_LEFT *= MOVE_LEFT ** LL
MOVE_LEFT *| MOVE_LEFT ** LL
MOVE_LEFT *# READING   ** DS

// 2. TRIMMING
TRIMMING *# TRIMMING ** SR
TRIMMING *= TRIMMING ** SR
TRIMMING *| TRIMMING_FIND_SECOND *= SR

TRIMMING_FIND_SECOND *= TRIMMING_FIND_SECOND ** SR
TRIMMING_FIND_SECOND *| TRIMMING_CLEANUP     ** SR

TRIMMING_CLEANUP *! TRIMMING_CLEANUP         *_ SR
TRIMMING_CLEANUP *_ MOVE_LEFT_UNTIL_NAIL_END ** SL

MOVE_LEFT_UNTIL_NAIL_END *_ MOVE_LEFT_UNTIL_NAIL_END ** SL
MOVE_LEFT_UNTIL_NAIL_END *| PLACE_NAIL_END           ** SD

PLACE_NAIL_END  *! TRIMMING_CLEANUP *| SR
PLACE_NAIL_END  *_ CHECK_ONE_LOWER  ** SD
CHECK_ONE_LOWER *! TRIMMING_CLEANUP *| SR
CHECK_ONE_LOWER *_ REMOVE_TOP_ROW   ** SS

// 3. REMOVE TOP ROW
REMOVE_TOP_ROW #* REMOVE_TOP_ROW ** US
REMOVE_TOP_ROW _* REMOVE_TOP_ROW_CLEANUP ** DS

REMOVE_TOP_ROW_CLEANUP !* REMOVE_TOP_ROW_CLEANUP _* RS
REMOVE_TOP_ROW_CLEANUP _* STOP ** SS
